<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-27T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-27T19:00:00-05:00" n="444" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d444">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. No. 763.72112/7645</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Chargé in Honduras</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CCB1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Curtis</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-27T19:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">March 27, 1918, 7 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Your March 21, 11 p.m. Department desires you to present substance of
                                its March 18, 4 p.m., to President of Honduras and considers it
                                advisable to obtain from him formal assurance as to elimination of
                                German interests, which you state you feel sure he will give if
                                requested.</p>
                            <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>